           perform   vis-ass-iva-des-000  thru vis-ass-iva-des-999    .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Plafond                                         *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   vis-imp-plf-000      thru vis-imp-plf-999        .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Imposta di bollo virtuale                       *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   vis-flg-ibv-000      thru vis-flg-ibv-999        .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
