      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   vis-svf-snx-000      thru vis-svf-snx-999        .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Si/no ritenuta d'acconto                        *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   vis-snx-rda-000      thru vis-snx-rda-999        .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * % ritenuta d'acconto                            *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   vis-per-rda-000      thru vis-per-rda-999        .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
