      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       vis-des-csr-000.
           move      "DS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "A"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      20                   to   v-car                  .
           move      08                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      37                   to   v-pos                  .
