      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       acc-cpv-aac-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Pre-accettazione                                *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Test se campo da accettare                  *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-ipc-sub-pgm-ind    =    "MP"
                     go to acc-cpv-aac-050
           else      go to acc-cpv-aac-999.
       acc-cpv-aac-050.
